        <div>
          <p>As a Contract Owner, you can:</p>
          <ul class="bulleted">
            <li>access your Contract information;</li>
            <li>change existing coverages;</li>
            <li>
              designate one or more Beneficiaries for each coverage; change the
              Contract Owner;
            </li>
            <li>change the Premium payment frequency;</li>
            <li>terminate your Contract or a coverage.</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            To exercise these rights, you must comply with the terms of the
            Contract and our administrative rules. Your rights may also be
            limited by the law governing the Contract.
          </p>

          <p>
            If you are more than one Owner, all must sign the request submitted
            to us.
          </p>
        </div>
